To bring up new menu    - Alt + Insert/ Cmd + n
to maximize window      - ctrl + shift + f12/ cmd + shift + f12
to run                  - ctrl + shift + f10/ cmd + shift + R
to move code up & down  - ctrl + shift + up/down / ctrl + shift + up/down



to give suggestions     - alt + enter/ option + enter

SEARCH EVERYWHERE
to find everywhere      - double shift
to find all the classes - ctrl + n
to find files           - ctrl + shift + n
to find symbols(methods
/ global variable)      - ctrl + shift + alt + n
find action             - ctrl + shift + a / cmd + shift + a

BASIC COMPLETION
to activate basic completion    -   ctrl + space
to complete a statement         -   ctrl + shift + enter
to see suggestions of static
constants or methods            -   ctrl + double space

EXPAND OR SHRINK THE CODE SELECTION
to select the word or expand
selection                       -   ctrl + w
to shrink the selection         -   ctrl + shift + w

COMMENTING
ctrl + slash

DUPLICATE OR DELETE LINES
to duplicate line               -   ctrl + d
to delete lines                 -   ctrl + y

MOVE CODE FRAGMENTS
to pull a line up/down          -   alt + shift + up/down
to pull a method up/down
(caret should be at method)     -   ctrl + shift + up/down

COLLAPSE
to collapse                     -   ctrl + minus
to collapse all                 -   ctrl + shift + minus

to expand                       -   ctrl + equals
to expand all                   -   ctrl + shift + equals

SURROUND AND UNWRAP
to surround/wrap the code
with some template              -   ctrl + alt + t

to unwrap to previous selection -   ctrl + shift + del

MULTIPLE SELECTIONS
to select symbol at caret
and next occurrence of symbol   -   alt + j

to deselect the last occurrence -   alt + shift + j

to select all occurrence of     -   ctrl + alt + shift + j
a symbol

TYPE MATCHING COMPLETION
to suggest or complete typ
matching syntax                 -   ctrl + shift + space

POSTFIX COMPLETION
to see postfix completion
suggestions                     -   .

COMPLETION WITH TAB
to replace the current value
with suggestion                 -   ctrl + space for suggestion and then press tab


RENAMING
to rename a file or a variable  -   shift + f6

EXTRACTING A VARIABLE
to extract a variable from
expression                      -   ctrl + alt + v

EXTRACT METHOD
to extract a method             -   ctrl + alt + m

REFACTORING MENU
to see a list of suggestions
for refactoring                 -   ctrl + alt + shift + t
to inline variable              -   ctrl + alt + n
to make variable constant       -   ctrl + alt + c

CODE FORMAT
to refactor a file or a block   -   ctrl + alt + l
to show refactor settings       -   ctrl + alt + shift + l

PARAMETER INFO
to see parameter info           -   ctrl + p

QUICK POPUPS
to see documentation            -   ctrl + q
to see method definition        -   ctrl + shift + i

EDITOR CODING ASSISTANCE
to go to highlighted
Error                           -   f2
